sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as ลูกค้า
    participant UI as machine-ui
    participant API as POST /api/buy/validate-coupon
    participant Inv as InventoryService
    participant CS as coupon_service

    User->>UI: กรอกโค้ด + ตะกร้า
    UI->>API: JSON code, cart, machine_code
    API->>Inv: check_stock(), compute_cart_subtotal()
    Inv-->>API: ok / fail
    API->>CS: lookup_coupon_by_code(), discount_and_final()
    CS-->>API: reason + Coupon | None
    API-->>UI: 200 {valid, discount_thb, final_thb, ...}
    UI-->>User: แสดงส่วนลดหรือข้อความไทย
